column1: Table S1: Surveyed locations and elevations of all stations deployed during summer of 2017 by personnel from UTEP. The seismic line discussed at length in this study use data from stations 1007--1057. A small number of stations were not surveyed with high precision GPS. We have omitted elevation values for those stations here. Locations and elevations are recorded in meters
column2: and positions are projected in WGS84 / UTM zone 8N (EPSG:32608).
